{"tid":588142,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣 合歡山清境交通一問","createTime":"2018-03-11T04:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T09:40:15.000Z","uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86b9a9f41ebe8a0920f034998f5100a348c632f9","tid":588142,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"小弟唔敢自駕遊 黎緊去台中<br />\n諗住搵日下午/夜晚出發去合歡山住一晚<br />\n朝早睇完日出就出發去清境農場<br />\n上網睇完都唔係好明d交通<br />\n大家有無經驗分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e79a4fd789448429d0f444a6a55d830c69f2944","tid":588142,"uid":11328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"試過5個人包車去"},{"pid":"cabdf9823599ada725e93f56af73eb174c3633ae","tid":588142,"uid":111241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"你真係住合歡山上面定係清景先 清景九成民宿都有日出團 事前會幫你叫旅遊巴車你上去清景 然後凌晨都有車帶你上山睇日出 至於去農場既巴士 清景遊客中心會有巴士時間表教你上去 巴士站啲站牌都list左啲路線 去到就明"},{"pid":"b5a9982b83e1644ecc1d9fab6d2ca746cb6353cd","tid":588142,"uid":119769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c45ab1a7aaf0d271c071edc1494db5b57286a42f","tid":588142,"uid":36486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"正常可以先住一晚清境 報民宿日出團 早上四點鐘左右出發 會睇星先 然後睇日出 睇完食早餐 想留多晚清境又得 離開清境又得"},{"pid":"a1cc051affd16ded9e834ea3d8b05b100c9626b0","tid":588142,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"你諗住包車定坐公車先？"},{"pid":"630c21108c67f299f9f41fb4056cd3422f7ac9af","tid":588142,"uid":153281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"統聯客運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e612ab4dbc6018521f1ca552da092424454b71d3","tid":588142,"uid":9971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"去清境農場記得睇清楚d巴士到站時間<br />\nD班次好疏 miss左有排等"},{"pi